ActExcise Act, 2001
PrecisREGULATIONS RESPECTING THE FEES FOR THE EXAMINATION OF INSTRUMENTS AND THE PROVISION OF TABLES which set out the fees to be paid to the Canada Customs and Revenue Agency for the examination and certification of instruments used in determining alcohol content for the purposes of calculating the amount of duty to be imposed, and take effect on July 1, 2003.
